{"id": 789, "genre": 1001, "title": "春节对抗无聊，你有什么好点子？", "description": "别说那些面见七大姑八大姨的丧气事儿了，说点有意思的经验。（题图来自：Janne Livonen）", "record_count": 4157, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194303kHntLQwJATRo6afZ.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-01T12:45:04Z", "options": [{"id": 45569, "content": "打麻将吹牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184177}, {"id": 45825, "content": "拼高达", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201125}, {"id": 46081, "content": "随意任性一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370200}, {"id": 45570, "content": "和朋友们谈一谈昨天今天和明天。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450703}, {"id": 45828, "content": "往死里吃，往死里听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58808}, {"id": 45830, "content": "听书啊～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448268}, {"id": 45831, "content": "欺负刚出生的外甥女", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422331}, {"id": 45835, "content": "upup", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451940}, {"id": 46347, "content": "陪家人聊聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454061}, {"id": 45580, "content": "??", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115358}, {"id": 45838, "content": "上豆瓣呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200005}, {"id": 45583, "content": "和同学组团去滑雪，吃火锅~", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445264}, {"id": 45839, "content": "还没想好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451952}, {"id": 45584, "content": "睡觉吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181845}, {"id": 45840, "content": "醉生梦死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 449164}, {"id": 46096, "content": "过年这天睡觉。不为什么，我想怎么编就怎么编", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453144}, {"id": 47376, "content": "其实最理想的就是看书，但是总是败给手机电脑，所以还是看想看的电影吧，然后在和各种同学，社团群撇哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460432}, {"id": 45841, "content": "想想自己今年的毕业旅行能不能和心爱的姑娘去", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403067}, {"id": 45842, "content": "窝在家里使劲睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451931}, {"id": 46098, "content": "做作业呗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448487}, {"id": 45587, "content": "刷日剧刷电影，不下雨就出去逛逛逛", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400760}, {"id": 47125, "content": "玩儿了老命地睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458708}, {"id": 45590, "content": "学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441466}, {"id": 46104, "content": "看好奇心，读one is all，听听落网，写写作业，吃喝拉撒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450612}, {"id": 46360, "content": "睡觉????", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448701}, {"id": 45849, "content": "旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392684}, {"id": 46617, "content": "拉她们打麻将！用激烈的战局堵上他们的?……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 455325}, {"id": 45850, "content": "做一个高三党应该做的事！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451979}, {"id": 45596, "content": "白天睡觉，晚上打炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 196312}, {"id": 45599, "content": "挑战不可能", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004737pxmY3sqjdZ5htvKc.jpg", "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374669}, {"id": 46112, "content": "跟妈妈学菜，让老爸带着兜风", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438575}, {"id": 46369, "content": "期末考试的成绩又可以拿出来晒了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402504}, {"id": 48417, "content": "手机涂色书（纸书涂着太麻烦~）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461690}, {"id": 49698, "content": "加班，加班，加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468274}, {"id": 45604, "content": "与三姑六婆斗智斗勇", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433026}, {"id": 46117, "content": "过年，联络同学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453261}, {"id": 45607, "content": "泡温泉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114353}, {"id": 45863, "content": "不上班就逛逛街，聊聊天，看看美剧，做做运动。上班就看好奇心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451992}, {"id": 45609, "content": "把魔都平时人最多的地方比如田子坊、新天地、淮海路,etc.逛一遍。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429884}, {"id": 45610, "content": "把你从小到大的好友和喜欢过的人写个单子...然后想方设法联系他们问一句新年好...", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363605}, {"id": 45868, "content": "只要睡过去那都不叫事儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 446691}, {"id": 46124, "content": "为新的美好的一年做一份规划，指定出目标。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453306}, {"id": 46636, "content": "写作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 455358}, {"id": 45614, "content": "搓麻将", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249226}, {"id": 46126, "content": "春节会无聊？会无聊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 452159}, {"id": 45615, "content": "斗地主好难呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450784}, {"id": 45616, "content": "向老爸学几道好菜，做给未来的媳妇儿吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450782}, {"id": 45872, "content": "不群发 不抢红包 关机养膘", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 436755}, {"id": 46896, "content": "看书+玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456710}, {"id": 45617, "content": "我就是来看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 317485}]}